column3: Manually tested `signrawtransaction` with explicit private key arguments on regtest, with P2SH-P2WSH. Works on this branch, and throws `Unable to sign input, invalid stack size` on master.\n\nAlso tested with a native P2WSH multisig for good measure. This already worked on master.
I do think this needs a test, but that can be done later (no need to hold up 0.16.0 for it), thanks @sjors for doing a manual test.
